{"tid":115360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵13年前也遭縱火 狂漢報復釀14人傷","createTime":"2017-02-10T13:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T13:42:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14431c000f5d2e3a9e14abefca6b18147c4733fa","tid":115360,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"香港地鐵13年前也遭縱火 狂漢報復釀14人傷<br />\n<br />\n2017/02/10 20:56&nbsp;984<br />\n<br />\n香港地鐵上一次發生列車車廂火警導致多人受傷，是2004年金鐘站列車縱火案，共成14人受傷。警方因接獲懲教署通知，稱嫌犯曾寫信向獄中友人表示有計劃炸毀港鐵，隔天迅速上門拘捕縱火的65歲男子嚴金鐘。嚴男後因證實患有妄想症，2006年被高等法院判處無期徒刑。案件發生在2004年1月5日，嚴男帶著多支火鍋用瓦斯罐和裝有香蕉水的塑膠罐，在早上7點30分尖峰時間，於荃灣站搭上一列駛向中環的港鐵列車。當列車駛離尖沙嘴過海到金鐘時，嚴在車廂內用打火機點燃一個裝有香蕉水的塑膠瓶，火勢迅速蔓延，車廂隨著濃煙密佈。嚴更試圖點燃瓦斯罐，所幸被人遏止。當列車駛至金鐘站時車長即時疏散乘客，嚴趁亂逃走。嚴被捕後供稱，因為政府允供他6輛改裝電動單車，存心要報復。他上庭時仍否認縱火，又指警方插贓嫁禍，並不時在庭上大叫法官是「魔鬼」、「賊官」和「砌生豬肉」。精神科醫生證實他有妄想症，認為他日後或做出危害社會的行為，最終法官判他終身監禁，最少服刑10年，是香港第一位純因縱火罪被判囚終身的犯人。<br />\n（國際中心／綜合外電報導）&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170210/1053614/香港地鐵13年前也遭縱火　狂漢報復釀14人傷\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170210%2F1053614%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B513%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E4%B9%9F%E9%81%AD%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E3%80%80%E7%8B%82%E6%BC%A2%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E9%87%8014%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d48821cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170210/1053614/香港地鐵13年前也遭縱火　狂漢報復釀14人傷</a>"},{"pid":"d9700095377869d1e6801bf50b01ae7dc3711871","tid":115360,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2783ba074e255fbbccafd0e0474e5944c6efcf7a","tid":115360,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:28:42.000Z","msg":"其實香港周街都係痴線佬"},{"pid":"437b4deaa026687c79f3385b5a185350caaa719e","tid":115360,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4f9c942c6c4e06ca019bb399f28299a89fe3646","tid":115360,"uid":47176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港周街都係痴線佬</blockquote><br />\n請問你以咩準則嚟計?"},{"pid":"527e7079f4cf3c5485a204063392153550e22f91","tid":115360,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"因為政府允供他6輛改裝電動單車，存心要報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39678fe8cd2b64de2734a0dab8a8d28f35438e3","tid":115360,"uid":23832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實香港周街都係痴線佬</blockquote><br />\n請問你以咩準則嚟計?</blockquote><br />\n因為佢本人就係其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169a19a86001540a6ea9d75ab7270b5a2c4f41ff","tid":115360,"uid":58090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為政府允供他6輛改裝電動單車，存心要報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n充公囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd81f1d8061d9e35821fb3f133da1e21ac9b9f6","tid":115360,"uid":7638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為政府允供他6輛改裝電動單車，存心要報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n充供，應該係"}]}